videos.headline: Lawrence scrambles left then drops dime to Ross for TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence rolls to his left then throws a pass on the run to Justyn Ross for the 30-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence scrambles left then drops dime to Ross for TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Clemson recovers Mond's fumble
videos.description: Texas A&M quarterback Kellen Mond gets the ball knocked loose and it is recovered by Clemson's James Skalski.

videos.headline: Higgins' great catch leads to Lawrence TD
videos.description: Tee Higgins makes a phenomenal catch at the 1-yard line, then a couple plays later Trevor Lawrence runs it in for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Higgins' great catch leads to Lawrence TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Dixon powers in for a Clemson TD
videos.description: Clemson running back Lyn-J Dixon runs through defenders and scores the 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dixon powers in for a Clemson TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Mond gets picked off by Clemson's Muse

videos.headline: Top ranked Clemson takes down Texas A&M 24-10
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence and the Clemson Tigers take down the Texas A&M Aggies 24-10 as they move to 2-0 on the season.
